@thierry-FreeBSD it doesn't include the FreeBSD fixes from https://github.com/TokTok/c-toxcore/pull/505. Once those are included (in 0.1.11?), it should compile on FreeBSD successfully.
@robinlinden don't forget to to do the thing (https://github.com/TokTok/c-toxcore/issues/569) after this is merged.
